description:
Political Correctness - short reading from Daniel Tammet's book

Just a short abridged reading from part of chapter 8 of Daniel Tammet's book &quot;Embracing the wide sky&quot;. Daniel is what's known as a &quot;prodigious autistic&quot;, gifted with a facility for mathematical and natural language learning. He knows his stuff. And this chapter points out the dangers of the language we are &quot;encouraged&quot; to adopt - the stifling language of political correctness.

